About this item

    This fits your .
  • Make sure this fits by entering your model number.
  • 10Gbps High Speed: UGREEN Cat 7 extender cable up to 10Gbps when matched with a Cat7 or higher ethernet cable, which is 10x faster than Cat6 extension cable. Fully meet your needs for online games, HD video streaming, uploading and downloading.
  • Extend the Ethernet Cable: When you have a high-speed network cable but the length is not enough, and it is too wasteful to buy a longer one. UGREEN Cat 7 extender cable will be your excellent choice. It can perfectly fit your network cable without any speed loss.
  • Wide Compatibility: With the RJ45 Connector, UGREEN Cat 7 extender cable can be perfectly compatible with computers, laptops, modems, routers, PS5, PS4, PS3, X-Box 360, X-Box One, networking switches, ADSL, network adapters, hubs, and other networking devices. It can also be fully backward compatible with Cat6e, Cat6, Cat5e, Cat5.
  • Durable and Reliable: UGREEN Cat 7 extension cables are made with 100% pure copper wire and gold-plated connectors, which can be very effective to reduce the loss during data transmission, making network speed faster and more stable. Sturdy male-to-female connectors with solid pins also make this network cable more durable with a longer lifespan.
  • Protect Ethernet Port: The network port of laptop damaged is a very troublesome thing. When you have UGREEN Cat 7 extension cable, you can use it instead of your laptop network port. Effectively protect your laptop's network port from damage due to plugging repeatedly.

Product Description

UGREEN Cat 7 Extender Cable

  • Extend your network cable, no need to re-purchase.
  • Protect the network port on the laptop from damage.
  • Perfectly compatible with most network cable type.
  • Cat 7 10Gbps high speed, meet all your needs.

Read more

Gold-plated Connector

The connector of the UGREEN Cat 7 network extender cable is made with gold-plated copper. It can greatly improve the transmission efficiency of the network cable, making the network speed faster and more stable.

Durable Material Design

UGREEN Cat 7 Ethernet extender cables are made of high-quality PVC material. The test proves that this internet extension cable can be bent at least 10000 times without broken, very suitable for long-term use.

100% Pure Copper Core

UGREEN Ethernet extender cable is made of 100% pure copper core. It can be very effective to reduce the loss during data transmission, keep the network cable high performance at all times.
